> Mike,
> There are several differences between each year. 1975 is the most specific
> and the most unique (but not at all a bad system), so in order to return
> your bus to stock, you will need to get a '75 harness. It has too many
> differences to list. The only years that are close enough to swap over are
> between '77 and '78.
> If you want to go original, I may have a nearly complete working '75 FI
> system, from the throttle body to the harness. PMail me if you are
> interested.
